\c 24
\s Ukumiswa kwesivumelwano
\p
\v 1 Yasisithi kuMozisi: Yenyukela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, wena loAroni, uNadabi loAbihu\x + 6.23; 28.1. Levi 10.1,2.\x*, labangamatshumi ayisikhombisa kubadala bakoIsrayeli\x + 24.9. Nani 11.16.\x*, likhonze likhatshana.
\v 2 Njalo uMozisi yedwa uzasondela eNkosini\x + 24.13,15,18.\x*, kodwa bona kabayikusondela; labantu kabayikwenyuka laye.
\v 3 UMozisi wasesiza wabatshela abantu wonke amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd* lokwahlulela konke; bonke abantu baphendula ngalizwi linye bathi: Wonke amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd* ewakhulumileyo sizawenza\x + 24.7; 19.8. Dute. 5.27.\x*.
\v 4 UMozisi wasebhala wonke amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Dute. 31.9.\x*. Wavuka ekuseni kakhulu, wakha ilathi phansi kwentaba, lensika ezilitshumi lambili, ngokwezizwe ezilitshumi lambili zakoIsrayeli\x + Gen. 28.18; 31.45; Eks. 23.24.\x*.
\v 5 Wathuma amajaha abantwana bakoIsrayeli, anikela iminikelo yokutshiswa, ahlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* iminikelo yokuthula yamajongosi\x + 20.24; 32.6.\x*.
\v 6 UMozisi wasethatha ingxenye yegazi\x + Heb. 9.18,19.\x*, wayifaka emiganwini; lengxenye yegazi wayifafaza phezu kwelathi\x + Heb. 9.18,19.\x*.
\v 7 Wasethatha incwadi yesivumelwano, wayibala ezindlebeni zabantu. Basebesithi: Konke iN\nd kosi\nd* ekutshiloyo sizakwenza silalele\x + 24.3.\x*.
\v 8 UMozisi wasethatha igazi, walifafaza phezu kwabantu\x + Heb. 9.19,20. Heb. 13.20. 1 Pet. 1.2.\x*, wathi: Khangelani igazi lesivumelwano iN\nd kosi\nd* esenze lani mayelana lawo wonke la amazwi.
\p
\v 9 Basebesenyuka oMozisi loAroni, uNadabi loAbihu, labangamatshumi ayisikhombisa kubadala bakoIsrayeli\x + 24.1.\x*,
\v 10 basebebona uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli\x + Gen. 18.2; 32.30. Hlu. 13.22. Isa. 6.1,5; Eks. 33.20,23. Joha. 1.18.\x*, langaphansi kwenyawo zakhe kwakukhona \add oku\add*njengomsebenzi \w wamasafire\w** agandelweyo\x + Hez. 1.26; 10.1.\x*, lanjengamazulu uqobo ngokucwengeka\x + Hlab. 89.44.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa kaselulanga isandla sakhe\x + 19.21.\x* kuzo iziphathamandla zabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Isa. 41.9.\x*. Sebembonile-ke uNkulunkulu badla banatha\x + Gen. 31.54; 18.12.\x*.
\s UMozisi usentabeni yeSinayi
\p
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yenyukela kimi entabeni\x + 24.2,15,18.\x*, ube khona; njalo ngizakunika izibhebhe zamatshe lomlayo lemithetho\x + 31.18; 32.15,16. Dute. 5.22.\x*, engikubhalileyo ukubafundisa.
\v 13 Wasukuma-ke uMozisi, lenceku yakhe uJoshuwa\x + 33.11. 17.9. 32.17.\x*; uMozisi wasesenyukela entabeni kaNkulunkulu\x + 24.2; 3.1.\x*.
\v 14 Wasesithi ebadaleni: Silindeleni lapha size sibuye kini; khangelani-ke uAroni loHuri balani\x + 17.10,12.\x*; olezindaba kasondele kubo\x + Gen. 37.19.\x*.
\v 15 UMozisi wasesenyukela entabeni, leyezi lasibekela intaba\x + 19.9,16. Mat. 17.5.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yahlala entabeni yeSinayi\x + 16.10. Nani 14.10.\x*; leyezi layisibekela insuku eziyisithupha; yasimbiza uMozisi ngosuku lwesikhombisa iphakathi kweyezi.
\v 17 Njalo ukubonakala kwenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* kwakunjengomlilo oqothulayo\x + 3.2.19.18. Dute. 4.36. Heb. 12.18,29.\x*, engqongeni yentaba, emehlweni abantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 18 UMozisi wasengena phakathi kweyezi, wenyukela entabeni; njalo uMozisi waba sentabeni insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane\x + 34.28. Dute. 9.9.\x*.